{"title":"Linux 命令","uid":"da48a0a1fb44d8749b7cfd67328a76d9","slug":"linux-command","date":"2022-08-21T07:51:41.589Z","updated":"2022-08-21T08:03:55.683Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/linux-command.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://pic.jitudisk.com/public/2022/08/21/26253e2551935.png","content":"<h3 id=\"linux-command\"><a href=\"#linux-command\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"linux command\"></a>linux command</h3><ul>\n<li><p>查看文件内容，并清屏显示</p>\n<pre><code>more -dc filename\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>more 命令也可以查看 nginx 的进程 id</p>\n<pre><code>more logs/nginx.pid\n</code></pre>\n<p>同 cat 命令</p>\n<pre><code>cat logs/nginx.pid\n</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>date命令</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">date</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#查看当前时间</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">date</span> -r filename <span class=\"token comment\">#查看文件最后的修改时间</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">date</span> -d yesterday <span class=\"token comment\">#字符串显示昨天的日期</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">date</span> +%Y-%m-%d <span class=\"token comment\">#格式化显示日期</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n<li><p>定时任务 crontab</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">crontab</span> -l <span class=\"token comment\">#linux 系统的定时任务，-l 列出定时任务的列表</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">crontab</span> -e <span class=\"token comment\">#-e 编辑定时任务列表</span>\n例子：\n* * * * * <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">command</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#每分钟执行一次，command 可以是命令也可以是脚本的路径</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">5</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> * * * /usr/local/nginx/logback.sh <span class=\"token comment\">#每天凌晨0点5分执行</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>系统服务，添加至开机启动 chkconfig</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">vim</span> /etc/init.d/nginxd <span class=\"token comment\">#编写可执行的脚本文件，放置于 /etc/init.d/ 下</span>\ninsert <span class=\"token string\">\"#chkconfig 2345 88 11\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">#在 nginxd 文件头部添加开机启动配置</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">chkconfig</span> nginxd <span class=\"token comment\">#添加至开机启动</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">#chkconfig 2345 88 11</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">2345</span> 表示开机启动的等级，即在什么情况下自动启动\n<span class=\"token number\">88</span>  代表开启服务的顺序，越大越晚启动\n<span class=\"token number\">11</span>  代表关闭服务的顺序，越小越晚关闭，\n    有些任务可能存在依赖关系，自写的服务，应晚启动、晚关闭<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n</li>\n<li><p>journalctl 检查系统日志 systemd</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">journalctl -xe <span class=\"token comment\">#从日志最下方开始，附带说明文本，可用于查看 keepalived 的运行日志</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"linux command 查看文件内容，并清屏显示 more -dc filename more 命令也可以查看 nginx 的进程 id more logs/nginx.pid 同 cat 命令 cat logs/nginx.pid date命令 date #查看当前时间 d...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":775,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Linux.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#linux-command\"><span class=\"toc-text\">linux command</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"东柳林","slug":"blo